role="switch" title="Switch to light theme" aria-checked="true" data-v-3e93ad3c data-v-f58534c0 data-v-409199d4><span class="check" data-v-409199d4><span class="icon" data-v-409199d4><!--[--><span class="vpi-sun sun" data-v-f58534c0></span><span class="vpi-moon moon" data-v-f58534c0></span><!--]--></span></span></button></div></div></div><div class="group" data-v-3e93ad3c><div class="item social-links" data-v-3e93ad3c><div class="VPSocialLinks social-links-list" data-v-3e93ad3c data-v-0c9dd10b><!--[--><a class="VPSocialLink no-icon" href="https://github.com/oh-my-live2d/oh-my-live2d" aria-label="github" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-v-0c9dd10b data-v-d0796310><span class="vpi-social-github" /></a><!--]--></div></div></div><!--]--><!--]--></div></div></div><!--[--><!--]--><button type="button" class="VPNavBarHamburger hamburger" aria-label="mobile navigation" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="VPNavScreen" data-v-ab480e08 data-v-d98f6572><span class="container" data-v-d98f6572><span class="top" data-v-d98f6572></span><span class="middle" data-v-d98f6572></span><span class="bottom" data-v-d98f6572></span></span></button></div></div></div></div><div class="divider" data-v-ab480e08><div class="divider-line" data-v-ab480e08></div></div></div><!----></header><!----><!----><div class="VPContent is-home" id="VPContent" data-pagefind-body data-v-2b8388d1 data-v-0df4cb2b><div class="VPHome" data-v-0df4cb2b data-v-68316c2c><!--[--><!--]--><div class="VPHero has-image VPHomeHero" data-v-68316c2c data-v-133db36b><div class="container" data-v-133db36b><div class="main" data-v-133db36b><!--[--><!--]--><!--[--><h1 class="name" data-v-133db36b><span class="clip" data-v-133db36b>OhMyLive2D</span></h1><p class="text" data-v-133db36b>Live2D For Web 组件</p><p class="tagline" data-v-133db36b>高可自定义且开箱即用的 Live2D For Web 组件, 快速为您的个人网站加入Live2D看板娘</p><!--]--><!--[--><!--]--><div class="actions" data-v-133db36b><!--[--><div class="action" data-v-133db36b><a class="VPButton medium brand" href="/guide/" data-v-133db36b data-v-9ac1ecc1>快速入门</a></div><div class="action" data-v-133db36b><a class="VPButton medium alt" href="https://github.com/oh-my-live2d/oh-my-live2d" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" data-v-133db36b data-v-9ac1ecc1>Github</a></div><!--]--></div><!--[--><!--]--></div><div class="image" data-v-133db36b><div class="image-container" data-v-133db36b><div class="image-bg" data-v-133db36b></div><!--[--><!--[--><!--[--><!--[--><img class="VPImage dark image-src" src="/logo-white.png" alt="logo" data-v-86c5d6f3><!--]--><!--[--><img class="VPImage light image-src" src="/logo-black.png" alt="logo" data-v-86c5d6f3><!--]--><!--]--><!--]--><!--]--></div></div></div></div><!--[--><!--]--><!--[--><!--]--><div class="VPFeatures VPHomeFeatures" data-v-68316c2c data-v-ff34cd3f><div class="container" data-v-ff34cd3f><div class="items" data-v-ff34cd3f><!--[--><div class="grid-3 item" data-v-ff34cd3f><div class="VPLink no-icon VPFeature" data-v-ff34cd3f data-v-47072814><!--[--><article class="box" data-v-47072814><div class="icon" data-v-47072814>📦</div><h2 class="title" data-v-47072814>开箱即用   ️</h2><p class="details" data-v-47072814>默认集成Cubism2.1和Cubism5, 无需手动导入其他任何第三方SDK</p><!----></article><!--]--></div></div><div class="grid-3 item" data-v-ff34cd3f><div class="VPLink no-icon VPFeature" data-v-ff34cd3f data-v-47072814><!--[--><article class="box" data-v-47072814><div class="icon" data-v-47072814>🛠️</div><h2 class="title" data-v-47072814>高可自定义</h2><p class="details" data-v-47072814>完全可自定义的样式, 灵活可配的菜单模块</p><!----></article><!--]--></div></div><div class="grid-3 item" data-v-ff34cd3f><div class="VPLink no-icon VPFeature" data-v-ff34cd3f data-v-47072814><!--[--><article class="box" data-v-47072814><div class="icon" data-v-47072814>💡</div><h2 class="title" data-v-47072814>多种使用场景</h2><p class="details" data-v-47072814>支持CDN与ESM两种导入方式, 支持多种文档构建工具中使用, 例如 vitepress、vuepress</p><!----></article><!--]--></div></div><!--]--></div></div></div><!--[--><!--]--><div class="vp-doc container" style="--vp-offset:calc(50% - Infinitypx);" data-v-68316c2c data-v-4327de71><!--[--><div style="position:relative;" data-v-68316c2c><div><h2 id="快速体验" tabindex="-1">快速体验 <a class="header-anchor" href="#快速体验" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;快速体验&quot;">​</a></h2><p>您可以通过<a href="https://stackblitz.com/edit/vitejs-vite-shccpw?file=main.js" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">stackblitz</a>在线体验</p><p>或者在任意项目使用 <code>CDN</code> 导入方式立即体验 <code>oh-my-live2d</code>:</p><img align="right" style="margin-left:10px;border-radius:10px;height:397px;" src="https://loclink-1259720482.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/image/%E5%BD%95%E5%B1%8F2024-03-21%2023.18.31.gif"><div class="language-html vp-adaptive-theme line-numbers-mode"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">html</span><pre class="shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark vp-code"><code><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">&lt;</span><span style="--shiki-light:#22863A;--shiki-dark:#85E89D;">script</span><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0;"> src</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">=</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">&quot;https://unpkg.com/oh-my-live2d@latest&quot;</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">&gt;&lt;/</span><span style="--shiki-light:#22863A;--shiki-dark:#85E89D;">script</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">&gt;</span></span>
